  "title": "SITE ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p><strong>JOB SCOPE</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for executing the company projects in building construction which covers.</li>\n  <li>To review project specifications and technical clarifications</li>\n  <li>To prepare method statements and check drawing discrepancies</li>\n  <li>To carry out project planning, design, material requisition, cost control, project supervision and documentation</li>\n  <li>To supervise the construction works and coordinate with client’s representatives, consultants and sub-contractors on technical matters</li>\n  <li>To target and ensure timely and smooth progress of works</li>\n  <li>To ensure quality of works is achieved and safety &amp; Environmental regulations are complied with</li>\n  <li>To ensure project activities complied with the Company’s ISO system</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Civil Structural Engineering recognized by Singapore Professional Engineers Board and BCA</li>\n  <li>Minimum 5 years working experience in building construction</li>\n  <li>Use of Autocad would be an advantage</li>\n  <li>Proficient in using Microsoft Office and familiar with Microsoft Project</li>\n  <li>Bilingual in English and Mandarin (to liaise with Mandarin speaking associates)</li>\n  <li>Good communicative skills, able to interact with people of all levels and teamwork</li>\n</ul>",
